								<p>The AFTT sell/buy interest rate is proprietary to AFTT and is governed by the General Business Terms. One clause relates to cost pass-through associated with external factors, such as changes in domestic and/or international monetary or credit policies affecting overall interest levels, or changes in the cost structure of liquidity providers and brokers.
